Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Abkhaz separatists have staged another 
adventure. Under the pretext of avoiding the spread of an 
infectious disease, they declared a quarantine on the whole of 
the territory of Gali rayon, thus making it impossible for 
relatives on either side of the Enguri river to visit each other. 

